# =========================================================================
# kruse-ai-scrape — root .gitignore
# =========================================================================

# --- Credentials (NEVER commit) ---
**/cookies.txt
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/cookies.txt.example

# --- Node ---
**/node_modules/
**/package-lock.json
*.log
*.tmp
*.pid

# --- Per-item MDs (huge — bundles in processed_mds/*.md are the published artifact) ---
**/processed_mds/threads/
**/processed_mds/articles/
**/processed_mds/blog/
**/processed_mds/blog_series/

# --- Scraper state (regenerable from source) ---
**/threads.json
**/threads.json.*.tmp
**/articles.json
**/articles.json.*.tmp
**/links/
**/raw_data/
**/fixtures/

# --- Logs ---
**/logs/*.log
**/logs/*.tmp
!**/logs/.gitkeep

# --- Per-tool local state (not project-relevant) ---
.claude/
.agents/
.codex/
.kiro/
plans/
skills-lock.json

# --- Editor / OS junk ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
